  title: Rampant Gangs
  description: Pontiff, dire news! Reports have reached our ears that a band of ruffians
    is harassing our followers in the bazaar. This would be naught but a common nuisance,
    were it not for the fact that they seem to target only the faithful of our fold.
    We have traced the root of this malice to a rival sect. How shall we act?
